DATA section is:
EN     (eV)   - neutron energy, low bound of zone
DATA   (barn) - (N,P)+(N,A) partial cross section
ERR    (barn) - total uncertainty
.Negative data values occur occasionally as a result
of the background corrections. These values are
consistent with zero within the experimental
uncertainty.  >>
for 17 resonances. Spin and total level widths are
